name: Adamant Key
description: An adamant key crafted especially for the gates in the mines.

description: Honey created from the pollen of hibiscus flowers, it's infused with healing properties.

name: Tulip Honey
description: Honey created from the pollen of tulip flowers, it revitalizes the spirit and restores mana.

name: Sun Flower Honey
description: Honey created from the pollen of sun flowers, it's infused with healing properties.

name: Lavender Honey
description: Honey created from the pollen of lavender flowers, it revitalizes the spirit and restores mana.

name: Honey
description: Can you bee-lieve how tasty this golden goop is?

name: Sugar
description: Everything is sweet if you put enough sugar on it.

name: Cheese
description: A wedge of fresh cheese, just waiting to cheese up any dish.

name: Caribbean Green Soup
description: A spicy soup popular in the Southern Isles.

name: Spicy Ramen
description: A bowl of noodles dressed spiced up with pepper.

name: BLT
description: A relatively simple, yet undeniably tasty, sandwich.

name: Honeyglazed Apple
description: A healthy, nutritious apple drenched in sugary honey. Yum!

name: Cinnamon Apple Pie
description: Apple pie with a cinnamon kick.

name: Peach Cobbler
description: Sweet peach slices with a crumbly topping, a dessert classic.

name: Spring Roll
description: Finely diced vegetables fried up in a thin dough wrapping.

name: Energy Smoothie
description: Imbued with a water crystal, this blend of fruits is a definite boost to your stamina.

description: Tomatoes cooked down into a juice. For all the sugar in it, it's still pretty bitter.

description: It's just milk and honey churned in ice, but it's irresistably delicious.

description: Yogurt and strawberries, layered together and topped with honeyed oats. Unbeatable when it comes to being quick, simple and delicious.

name: Omelet
description: A basic egg dish, great for breakfast. Or lunch. Or dinner. Or whenever!

description: Deep fried fish served with a side of chips, can you believe some people actually call them "fries"?!

description: Soft chunks of delicate lobster meat, swimming in a thick and creamy soup.

description: Many a beginner chef's first dish, its simplicity does not subtract from its yummyness.

description: Onion slices, breaded and fried in oil. Vegetables don't taste better than this.

name: Sweet and Spicy Shrimp
description: Sweetness and spiciness battle each other for dominance in this shrimp dish. The winner of their duel? Your tastebuds.

name: Poke Bowl
description: Seasoned fish served over rice, simple fare often enjoyed by sailors while out at sea.

description: Roast mushrooms, drenched in a thick and savory broth. A peasant meal, but still fit for a king.

name: Veggie Wrap
description: Diced veggies wrapped in a corn tortilla, the soft wrap contrasts well against the crunchy vegetables inside.

name: Trail Mix
description: A mix of energy-boosting food to keep one fueled over long adventures.

name: Churros
description: Dough sticks, fried in oil and breaded with sugar. Simple, yet very delicious.

name: Custard
description: A jiggly dessert that was once the food of wealthy lords. These days anyone can afford to make it.

name: Elven Health Book
description: An ancient tome of Elven script, detailing how to increase one's vitality.

name: Charcoal
description: A piece of sooty charcoal. When it comes to writing, it'll work better than nothing.
